  <h3>Lore</h3>
  <p>Ancient protectors of the desert tombs, these beetle-like monsters unleash powerful electrical bursts when struck, punishing melee attackers severely.</p>
  <h3>Notable Drops</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Normal:</strong> Javelins, minor mana potions</li>
    <li><strong>Nightmare:</strong> Rare boots, runes (Amn–Sol)</li>
    <li><strong>Hell:</strong> Unique gloves, runes (Um–Ist)</li>
  </ul>
  <h3>Affixes</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Prefix:</strong> Charged – Extra lightning pulse</li>
    <li><strong>Suffix:</strong> of Static – Pulses electricity every few seconds</li>
  </ul>
